</i><br><i>I wonder if it’s true what they 
</i><br><i>don’t wear beneath the kilt
</i><br>
</p><p>They crept up on that sleeping Scotsman 
<br>quiet as could be
<br>Lifted up his kilt 
<br>about an inch so they could see
<br>And there behold, for them to view, 
<br>beneath his Scottish skirt
<br>Was nothing more than God 
<br>had graced him with upon his birth
<br>
