</i><br>
</p><p>They marveled for a moment, 
<br>then one said we must be gone
<br>Let’s leave a present for our friend, 
<br>before we move along
<br>As a gift they left a blue silk ribbon, 
<br>tied into a bow
<br>Around the bonnie star, 
<br>the Scots kilt did lift and show
<br>
